    "These mechanisms allow only a very restricted set of carefully crafted jailbreak prompts to bypass their defenses.",
    "This highlights the need for further research into crafting highly effective prompts.",
    "C. Ablation Study (RQ4)We carry out an ablation study to gauge each component's contribution to MASTERKEY's effectiveness.",
    "We create two variants for this study: MASTERKEY-NO-FINETUNE, and MASTERKEY-NO-REWARD.",
    "They are fine-tuned but lack reward-ranked fine-tuning."
